Package com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport

Contains classes for communicating provenance information with Intelligence Analysis Platform services.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CardProvenance The provenance of the data on a Card that an Item in the Intelligence Analysis Platform contains.
OriginIdentifier A container for information that uniquely identifies the data that the CardProvenance with this OriginIdentifier describes, in its original data source.
RetrievalBlock An collection of RetrievalDatums that together contain all the information necessary for the Intelligence Analysis Platform to retrieve the data for a Card from a particular external source.
RetrievalBlockGlobalIdentifier A container for information that uniquely identifies a RetrievalBlock across multiple CardProvenances.
RetrievalBlockIdentifier A container for information that uniquely identifies a RetrievalBlock within its containing CardProvenance.
RetrievalDatum A key-value pair that contains some or all of the information that the Intelligence Analysis Platform uses to retrieve data from an external source.
 

Package com.i2group.apollo.model.provenance.transport Description
